{"tid":1305601,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"全宇宙最仆街既練馬師兼師傅","createTime":"2019-07-11T01:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T04:10:08.000Z","uid":40938,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"409fa4bf9a772098e88561ceb7ba3576003e11d3","tid":1305601,"uid":40938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"係告東尼<br />\n<br />\n今朝睇馬季煞科排位表，一如所料冇牙晉份，我地已經冇機會再睇牙晉綠上飛馳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇返紀錄，牙晉告別戰已經一早上演左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我不停同自己講，冇事既，已經接受左事實，佢咁廢冇得玩係正常<br />\n但到左最後嗰刻黎到，真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6Rofd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6Rofd5.png&h=ab831a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母告狗告東尼，唔好話做師傅，做人你都有問題啦<br />\n最後一隻俾徒弟騎已經係5月5號，有冇搞撚錯呀<br />\n你老尾有好馬就俾晒隻死nigga，依家隻死nigga好撚勁咩屌你，攞位又垃圾推騎又on9<br />\n唔撚識教徒弟就咪撚收啦，害撚死人，有得操永遠冇得騎，屌你老母，仲好意思用自己個名命名個告東尼獎，有冇諗過牙晉感受<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad76343818bc8c334fc6b31c41691569bc5dbb48","tid":1305601,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:48:26.000Z","msg":"人至義盡"},{"pid":"dc93bb64cce3b68fbbad347a3a03d1730fe59e47","tid":1305601,"uid":173179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:52:57.000Z","msg":"仁至義盡啦<br />\n呢個便宜仔黎，唔好唔記得<br />\n果陣告直頭比埋馬克羅斯佢騎，想佢起機都衰左"},{"pid":"2ef470949fd9d4c4debabf55dc3b4cc1326b6445","tid":1305601,"uid":8441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc93bb64cce3b68fbbad347a3a03d1730fe59e47","tid":1305601,"uid":173179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:52:57.000Z","msg":"仁至義盡啦<br />\n呢個便宜仔黎，唔好唔記得<br />\n果陣告直頭比埋馬克羅斯佢騎，想佢起機都衰左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"牙晉幫馬克開光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"